                    "caption": "<center>Fig. 3.1 </center>",
                    "page": 10
                }
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\\(R_{\\mathrm{p}}\\) has a resistance of \\(4.0\\Omega\\) . Use Fig. 3.3 and the values in Table 3.1 to support your answer.",
